{"tid":1792100,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【失敗乃成功之母】吳尊喜見女兒成長　9歲NeiNei領悟比賽真諦","createTime":"2019-12-21T11:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T15:51:05.000Z","uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"117ec365259cd58795bc68b15ea8a1a157524f65","tid":1792100,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T11:19:51.000Z","msg":"【失敗乃成功之母】吳尊喜見女兒成長 9歲NeiNei領悟比賽真諦<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2525000/2525804/ng_thumb_20191221_E_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2525000%2F2525804%2Fng_thumb_20191221_E_1024.jpg&h=fd99a0fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 吳尊女兒NeiNei參加芭蕾舞比賽。<br />\n<br />\n早年，吳尊曾帶大女NeiNei一同為《爸爸回來了》及《爸爸去哪兒》做嘉賓，令年紀少少的NeiNei大受歡迎。現時，NeiNei已9歲大，雖然已甚少公開露面，但熱愛芭蕾舞的她不時參加比賽，最近更開通Instagram分享生活。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2525000/2525804/20191221neinei1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2525000%2F2525804%2F20191221neinei1_1024.jpg&h=cfaa0305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 「Result is out! Sometimes we win, sometimes we learn new things, AND I DID!!!」（Instagram圖片）<br />\nNeiNei自3歲半起便參加真人騷《爸爸回來了》，後又參加《爸爸去哪兒》，一炮而紅，不少觀眾都大讚NeiNei非常可愛。<br />\n<br />\n不過，近年NeiNei都減少拍節目，除專心學業外，她也非常熱衷於跳芭蕾舞，不時到外地比賽跳舞。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2525000/2525804/20191221neinei2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2525000%2F2525804%2F20191221neinei2_1024.jpg&h=72606fcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ NeiNei每天都為比賽練習，非常熱衷跳芭蕾舞。（微博圖片）<br />\n今午，吳尊就在微博分享NeiNei日前到馬來西亞參加比賽的照片，並指女兒與好友也一起開通了個人Instagram分享生活。<br />\n<br />\nNeiNei在Instagram上分享比賽的照片，並指「Result is out! Sometimes we win, sometimes we learn new things, AND I DID!!!」雖然比賽落敗，但她沒有因而氣餒，也學習到新的東西。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2525000/2525804/20191221neinei3_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2525000%2F2525804%2F20191221neinei3_1024.jpg&h=aff6b64e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 吳尊見證女兒成長，非常感動。（微博圖片）<br />\n吳尊表示看到NeiNei的成長大為感動，並在微博有感而發：<br />\n<br />\nNeiNei最近和她一幫芭蕾舞的好友一起開了IG..... 今天看到她寫的博文，讓我太驚訝了<br />\n<br />\n每一次跟他說這句話，他都說Papa, I want to win&hellip;&hellip; 知道她有默默把我說的話聽進去，超級超級開心<br />\n<br />\n這次沒進決賽，她難過但沒哭，還承認自己不够好！Nothing worth having comes easy... NeiNei，加油<br />\n<br />\nNeiNei對比賽的態度令吳尊大感欣慰，不再重視賽果而是重視比賽的過程，這種心態比獎項來得重要，難怪吳尊如此快樂！"},{"pid":"f3042a016a5c1a22973d28db575c301427e3c453","tid":1792100,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T11:20:13.000Z","msg":"【行動po】【求推】點解1223去稅局 連登冇人講？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1792093\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1792093</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3BnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=8c737967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3BnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=b9cc51a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"b37b22b3ff2580ca1430f0adb8e6a8552d188abc","tid":1792100,"uid":283071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T15:51:05.000Z","msg":"失望！完全唔似鍾嘉欣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}